OL,5, A US high school is facing criticism   
OL,6, after it suspended a student for       
OL,7, recording her teacher using a racial   
OL,8, slur in class.                         
OL,10,FMary Walton, 15, filmed her teacher    
OL,11,Fsaying the n-word repeatedly on 9 May  
OL,12,Fat Glendale High School in Springfield,
OL,13,FMissouri.                              
OL,15,FHer family has since retained a lawyer 
OL,16,Fand asked the school to apologise.     
OL,18,FSchool officials said they believe the 
OL,19,Fstudent was disciplined appropriately. 
OL,20,FThe teacher who used the slur has quit.
